> Problem: [2442. 反转之后不同整数的数目](https://leetcode.cn/problems/count-number-of-distinct-integers-after-reverse-operations/description/)

[TOC]

# 思路
> hash + 一次遍历 

# 复杂度
- 时间复杂度: 
> $O(n)$

# Code
```C []

int reversal(int x)
{
    int res = 0;
    while (x) {
        res = res * 10 + x % 10;
        x = x / 10;
    }

    return res;
}
int countDistinctIntegers(int* nums, int numsSize){
    int i, t, ans = 0, hash[1000001] = {0};

    for (i = 0; i < numsSize; i++) {           
        if (!hash[nums[i]]) {
            ans++;
            hash[nums[i]] = 1;
        }

        t = reversal(nums[i]);  
        if (!hash[t]) {
            ans++;
            hash[t] = 1; 
        }
    }

    return ans;
}
```
